-- Brad Childress Is Fired as Minnesota Vikings' Coach After 3-7 NFL Start
-- B y   L a r r y   S i d d o n s
-- 2010-11-22T17:23:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-22/brad-childress-is-fired-as-minnesota-vikings-coach-after-3-7-nfl-start.html
Brad Childress was fired today as
coach of the Minnesota Vikings after a 3-7 start to the National
Football League season.  Leslie Frazier was named interim coach for the rest of the
season, the Vikings said in a news release.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  